Package: pvac
Type: Package
Title:  PCA-based gene filtering for Affymetrix arrays
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2010-12-30
Author: Jun Lu and Pierre R. Bushel
Maintainer: Jun Lu <lujun@niehs.nih.gov>, Pierre R. Bushel <bushel@niehs.nih.gov>
Description: The package contains the function for filtering genes by the proportion of variation accounted for by the first principal component (PVAC).
License: LGPL (>= 2.0)
Imports: affy (>= 1.20.0), stats, Biobase
Depends: R (>= 2.8.0)
Suggests: pbapply, affydata, ALLMLL, genefilter
biocViews: Bioinformatics, Microarray, OneChannel, QualityControl
LazyLoad: yes

